hEllo Npm 



Create:
      
        mkdir package
        cd package 

        git init 

        ... 
        ... 
        git add -u origin master

        npm init 

        npm link 
      
      if every things ok? then publish it to npm 
      >   npm publish



Testing:

        npm link 

        npm link <package-name>



        npm unlink 
        
    Happy Code!   we can serach our packages in NPM

Install: 

        npm i yagyaworld
        
        
        
         const today = new Date();
  const f = new Intl.DateTimeFormat("en-us", {
    dateStyle: "full",
    timeStyle: "full",
    // dayPeriod: "long"
  });

  console.log(f.format(today));
        
        

